caption: Watching the revered star cast of Late. Ramanand Sagar ji’s Ramayana, including @siyaramkijai as Ram ji, @dipikachikhliatopiwala as Sita ji, and @sunil_lahri as Lakshman ji, resurrects cherished memories of childhood spent with family, engrossed in the epic saga. Commencing with eager anticipation, the fourth day of Chhath Puja, termed “Usha Arghya,” sees devotees awakening at dawn to perform rituals by water bodies. Clad in traditional attire, they engage in a profound expression of gratitude to the rising sun, standing in water and offering obeisance. The day encapsulates themes of spiritual purification and the renewal of life-sustaining energy drawn from the sun god. As the sun ascends, meticulous cleaning of worship spaces precedes the heartfelt ceremonies. The conclusion is marked by communal gatherings for joyous feasts, solidifying the sense of community and reverence for the celestial deity. 😍🙏 #therawtextures #bigindianwanderers #chhathpuja #chhathmahaparv #bihari #chhath #bihar

Our visit to Delhi’s Tulip Garden was an enchanting experience, immersed in a breathtaking display of vibrant colors. Rows of meticulously arranged tulips stretched endlessly, showcasing a mesmerizing array of fiery reds and soft pastels. Each flower captivated us with its intricate details, from delicate petals to subtle color variations, while the sweet fragrance of blossoms filled the air. As we explored, we were drawn to particular patches, each exuding its unique charm, and we marveled at the care and attention that crafted such a serene atmosphere. Our time in the garden was a testament to the beauty of nature, leaving us with cherished memories to treasure. 😍😊 #therawtextures #bigindianwanderers #tulips #tulipseason #tulipfestival #delhidiaries #meandyou 🧿

A visit to the Rock Garden Chandigarh. 😍😎 

- The Rock Garden in Chandigarh is a captivating blend of art and nature. Its intricate sculptures made from recycled materials are a testament to human creativity. Don’t miss the Waterfall Area, Nek Chand’s House, and the various themed sections like the Kingdom of God, Courtyard, and Maze. It’s a must-visit for anyone seeking inspiration and wonder in Chandigarh’s cultural landscape. 😍😊 
The swing area offers a nostalgic and whimsical experience, perfect for visitors of all ages to relive childhood memories while enjoying the scenic beauty of the garden. 🤗🤗 
The serene atmosphere and lush greenery provide a tranquil escape from the hustle and bustle of the city. Whether you’re an art enthusiast, nature lover, or simply looking for a unique experience, the Rock Garden offers something truly special for every visitor. 😍🤗 #therawtextures #bigindianwanderers #chandigarh #rockgarden #couplegoals #lovestory #recycledart
